<li><span class="citation book" id="CITEREFHarry2000b">Harry, Bill (2000b). <i>The John Lennon Encyclopedia</i>. Virgin. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/978-0-7535-0404-8" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-7535-0404-8">978-0-7535-0404-8</a>.</span></li>
