<li><span class="citation book" id="CITEREFNorman2008">Norman, Philip (2008). <i>John Lennon: The Life</i>. ECCO (Harper Collins). <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/978-0-06-075401-3" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-06-075401-3">978-0-06-075401-3</a>.</span></li>
