<li><span class="citation book" id="CITEREFSpizer2005">Spizer, Bruce (2005). <i>The Beatles Solo on Apple Records</i>. 498 Productions, LLC. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/978-0-9662649-5-1" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-9662649-5-1">978-0-9662649-5-1</a>.</span></li>
